\int\dif^{3}xe^{-i\vec{p}\vec{x}}\left(i\partial_{t}+\omega_{p}\right)\phi\left(x\right)=\sqrt{2\omega_{p}}a_{p}\left(t\right)e^{-i\omega_{p}t}
